      "content": "honestly i cant even look at the news anymore. everything everywhere is just burning or flooding or dying... it feels like we are all just watching a slow motion car crash. what is the point of even trying to plan a future or build a life when the world is just fundamentally broken and doomed anyway? it feels so pointless.",
